      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "__Trios__\nNearly identical to Duos but the support player will carry all medkits and a shotgun so everyone can play heal off.\n__Squads__\nDon't do this. Identical to trios but second fragger should also focus on medkits and IGL and main frag should get rotation and surge tags.",
